data.description: Enjoy the peace and quiet that comes with this updated Ranch style house that sits on 5.62 acres. You will find this property has mature pecan trees through out. Perfect home for family get togethers. Inside this home you will find an open floorpan with four good sized bedrooms. You will enjoy the spacious kitchen with plenty of cabinets. This property has had many modern upgrades to appreciate. This house has a separate garage with a workspace that can be converted into many things. Enjoy sitting on the covered back porch observing the many wildlife that visits this property.
